comments.body:
Quick and dirty one-off
`for $i in distinct-values(//physloc[@type='code'][.='review']/../@id[matches(., '_n')]/substring-before(., '_n')), $j in distinct-values(//physloc/../@id[matches(., '_i')]/substring-before(., '_i')) return $i[.=$j]`
gives
C0079
C0640
RBD1
C1413
C0059
C0688
AC297
C0262
C0129
C0763
AC195
AC180
MC174
MC016
Sent a report of containers not linked to a container entity within those collections.
